		Minimum 3 years&#39; experience in Software Development</li>
	<li>
		Intimate knowledge of UIKit, Cocoa Touch, and Xcode.</li>
	<li>
		Experience with Core Data and Core Graphics Frameworks.</li>
	<li>
		A keen attention to detail and a passion for translating beautiful designs into functional code.</li>
	<li>
		Ability to communicate with clients and make technology recommendations based on best of breed solutions.</li>
	<li>
		Experience developing in teams and using source control software like Git.</li>
	<li>
		Strong understanding of MVC concepts, Design Patterns, and Object Oriented Programmingï»¿.</li>
